{"tid":2162734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【外行導演】駐港部隊惠州艦操練「錯漏百出」 炮手冇戴頭盔被指想欺敵","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T11:56:08.000Z","uid":281769,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a831fc7a93d50218feb6541b04c7da200c5633a3","tid":2162734,"uid":281769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200818/LNFHKJAETNFFRPNXVZZEYT5IWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200818%2FLNFHKJAETNFFRPNXVZZEYT5IWQ%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=16080fd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200818%2FLNFHKJAETNFFRPNXVZZEYT5IWQ%2F&h=c80cf348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200818/LNFHKJAETNFFRPNXVZZEYT5IWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n（新增內容）中國官方社交媒體發佈解放軍駐港部隊艦艇大隊導彈護衞艦「惠州艦」，近日在南海海域展開多項海上軍事訓練的影片，意圖展示實力，甚至震懾「外敵」的意思。不過，台灣「中華戰略學會」研究員張競卻發現惠州艦的官兵在操練錯漏百出，他質疑，解放軍故意發放影片「鬧笑話」，存心欺敵。"},{"pid":"b9de7dfa4e223a4aafc4a8e13198cebbbcf52d98","tid":2162734,"uid":62721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"個頭盔仲值錢過d士兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cd8b8dde88b68bb7af00e71b8ac913191c38ba","tid":2162734,"uid":295477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"個頭硬過碌尻怕閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Afnmev.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Afnmev.png&h=0290326d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a095d0f64a9a8cf4aff740816f983eb096317a6","tid":2162734,"uid":67179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"連呢D基本野都做唔到就知無得同美國打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75705d3d930d1012a57d4ad03e301803ac45f3fd","t